titles.title: A bill to designate the Federal building located at the corner of North 29th Street and Fourth Avenue North in Billings, Montana, as the "William J. Jameson Federal Building", and for other purposes.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S56-57)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Environment and Public Works.

bill.summary: 1/25/1994--Introduced. Designates the Federal building located at the corner of North 29th Street and Fourth Avenue North in Billings, Montana, as the William J. Jameson Federal Building.
